<h2>0.5.0</h2>

<h3>New features</h3>

<ul>
<li>ðŸŽ‰ <a href="https://bulma.io/documentation/elements/tag/#list-of-tags" rel="nofollow">List of tags</a></li>
<li>New <strong>variable naming system</strong>: <code>component</code>-<code>subcomponent</code>-<code>state</code>-<code>property</code></li>
<li>Improved <strong>customization</strong> thanks to new set of variables</li>
<li>#934 New <code>.is-shadowless</code> helper</li>
</ul>

