<h2>0.0.23</h2>

<h3>BREAKING</h3>

<ul>
<li><code>bulma</code> folder renamed to <code>sass</code> to avoid the redundant <code>bulma/bulma</code> path</li>
<li><code>variables.sass</code> moved to <code>/utilities</code></li>
<li>almost everything is singular now</li>
<li><strong>elements</strong> only have one class</li>
<li><strong>components</strong> have at least one sub-class</li>
<li><code>.content</code> moved to elements</li>
<li><code>.table</code> moved to elements</li>
<li><code>.message</code> moved to components</li>
<li><code>.table-icon</code>, <code>.table-link</code>, <code>.table-narrow</code> are now called <code>.is-icon</code>, <code>.is-link</code>, <code>.is-narrow</code></li>
</ul>

<h3>Added</h3>

<ul>
<li>all variables are now <code>!default</code> so you can set your custom variables before importing Bulma</li>
</ul>

